title: Call for Papers Time
brief: The GDG Munich DevFest is coming up! 2015 we held a very popular "DevFest" and now it is 2016 and we are back again!Mark the dates! #GDGMunich will host Devfest2016, a developer conference, on November.We are looking motivated speakers for the conference, speakers who would like to share their wisdom on topics around modern development and/or various technologies with us. [Submit your Proposal](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdjznT01uNIMrSlGPKjizFcuNtpI5YUvLZQjhP8UkLauom1Zg/viewform). Call for Papers will end November 1!

title: First speakers for the GDG devfest, Munich
brief: Today we are lucky to announce our first speakers for our upcoming devfest!
